  "title": "Event Assistant!!",
  "description": "<p>🌟Event Assistant-Join the team now!!🌟<br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for organized, helpful, and energetic individuals to join our team as Event Assistants. In this role, you will support the event team with planning, setup, on-site operations, and pack-down. This position is perfect for someone who enjoys working with people and contributing to smooth, successful events.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Help maintain a clean, organized, and safe event environment</li><li>Communicate with team members to ensure smooth event flow</li><li>Perform general administrative or support tasks when needed</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Good communication and teamwork skills</li><li>Organized, proactive, and willing to learn</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Reliable, punctual, and flexible with working hours</li><li>Able to stand for long periods and handle light physical tasks</li></ul>",
